section_title: REPORTING AND REVIEW OF INFORMATION FROM ANNEX I PARTIES UNDER THE PROTOCOL:
sentences: Dominique Blain (Canada) will conduct informal consultations. PROTOCOL ARTICLE 3.14 (ADVERSE EFFECTS): Parties established a joint SBI/SBSTA contact group, co-chaired by Andrew Ure (Australia) and Eduardo Calvo Buendía (Peru). INTERNATIONAL TRANSACTION LOG (ITL).
The SBI agreed to take note of this information.
